OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FDetectives are appealing for further
OL,7,Fvictim-survivors to come forward after
OL,8,Fa man from Ilford has been sentenced
OL,9,Ffor 17 offences, including rape,
OL,10,Fblackmail and making indecent images
OL,11,Fof children.
OL,13,FOn Friday Waleed Saeed, 31, was jailed
OL,14,Ffor 16 years years following a Met
OL,15,Finvestigation that uncovered his
OL,16,Fextensive offending, in which he
OL,17,Ftargeted and sexually assaulted young
OL,18,Fmen of Muslim background.
OL,20,FPolice believe there could be a
OL,21,Ffurther 90 victims out there.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
