PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781891299
OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FDetective Constable Peter Collington,
OL,7,Fwho led the Met's investigation, said:
OL,8,F"We know Saeed began offending in
OL,9,F2018, deliberately targeting young men
OL,10,Ffrom south Asian and Muslim
OL,11,Fbackgrounds on the impression that
OL,12,Fthese victim-survivors would be less
OL,13,Flikely to contact police.
OL,15,F"Following his sentence, I am making a
OL,16,Fdirect appeal to other victim-
OL,17,Fsurvivors who may not have had the
OL,18,Fconfidence to come forward, to please
OL,19,Fcontact us.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781891299
OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,F"We want to be absolutely clear that
OL,7,Fno one should ever have their
OL,8,Fsexuality exploited or weaponised
OL,9,Fagainst them in this way. You will be
OL,10,Ftreated with compassion, sensitivity
OL,11,Fand absolute confidentiality."
OL,13,FThe Met are urging people to call 101
OL,14,Fand quote 5335/18JUNE2026 if you, or
OL,15,Fsomeone you know, has been impacted by
OL,16,Fthis case.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
