OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FThe investigation began in August 2024
OL,7,Ffollowing reports of a rape in a
OL,8,FLondon park. The victim said they had
OL,9,Fexchanged sexual images with someone
OL,10,Fhe believed to be a transgender woman.
OL,11,FShortly afterwards, he received
OL,12,Fthreatening messages from another
OL,13,Faccount run by Saeed, revealing his
OL,14,Ftrue identity as a man. He demanded
OL,15,Fpayment, otherwise the images would be
OL,16,Freleased.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781891299
OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FWhen the victim said he could not pay,
OL,7,FSaeed demanded that they met in person
OL,8,For he would release the images. Over
OL,9,Fthe following weeks, Saeed coerced the
OL,10,Fvictim into attending three separate
OL,11,Fmeetings in a London park late at
OL,12,Fnight where he sexually assaulted and
OL,13,Fraped the victim. He wore a face
OL,14,Fcovering to conceal his identity.
OL,16,FFollowing this report, officers
OL,17,Flaunched extensive digital enquiries
OL,18,Fand were able to trace these accounts
OL,19,Fback to Saeed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
