CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781891299
OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FIn November 2024, he was arrested and
OL,7,Ftwo mobile phones were seized. A
OL,8,Fforensic examination of these not only
OL,9,Ffound the social media accounts used
OL,10,Fto target the victim, but also
OL,11,Funcovered further intimate images
OL,12,Flinked to additional, unidentified
OL,13,Fvictims, some of whom were believed to
OL,14,Fbe children.
OL,16,FSaeed was subsequently charged with
OL,17,Feight counts of rape, blackmail and
OL,18,Fthreatening to share a photograph or
OL,19,Ffilm of a person in an intimate state
OL,20,Fon 19 November 2024. He was remanded
OL,21,Finto custody immediately.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
