OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FUpon identifying the potential for
OL,7,Ffurther victims, detectives undertook
OL,8,Fextensive cross-checks of non-recent
OL,9,Fcases where they found a series of
OL,10,Freports linked to Saeed, dating back
OL,11,Fto 2018 from within London and other
OL,12,Fareas of the UK.
OL,14,FThese cases followed the same pattern
OL,15,Fwhereby Saeed would pose as a woman or
OL,16,Ftransgender woman online, obtain
OL,17,Fintimate images and then blackmail his
OL,18,Fvictims. In some cases, coercing them
OL,19,Finto meeting in-person where further
OL,20,Fserious sexual offences were committed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
