OL,3,CDetectives appeal for further victim-
OL,4,Csurvivors in sextortion case
OL,6,FSaeed was then charged with a further
OL,7,Fnine counts related to four additional
OL,8,Fvictims on 25 March 2025.
OL,10,FHe pleaded guilty at Snaresbrook Crown
OL,11,FCourt on Monday 2nd March to the
OL,12,Ffollowing charges, relating to four
OL,13,Fvictims:
OL,15,FOn Thursday 12th March a jury found
OL,16,Fhim guilty of:
OL,18,FThe trial took place at Snaresbrook
OL,19,FCrown Court, with offences relating to
OL,20,Fthe fifth victim-survivor.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/8
